ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectDesignated Barley ** August 2010 - July 2011 INITIAL PAYMENTS **
PrecisOrder a) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2010-1491 of November 25, 2010; and b) approving the increase by the Canadian Wheat Board of the initial payments for grades other than the base grade of DESIGNATED BARLEY for the pool period commencing on August 1, 2010 and ending on July 31, 2011.
